# =================== libunwind =====================
#
# !!! This is NOT robust !!!
# !!! specific CPPFLAGS not set because externals version is assumed
# !!!  (the -I for externals is already part of the CPPFLAGS
#
# !!! also, LDFLAGS does not need a -L component for an analogous reason

